    "Furthermore, the SMD value of 0.57 also further reveals the enhancement effect of this teaching mode on students' creativity.",
    "As shown in Fig. 7, the impact of project-based learning on students' collaboration skills reached a medium to large effect size (SMD = 0.66, Z = 5.91, P < 0.001), indicating that project-based learning can effectively enhance students' teamwork abilities.",
